# forge-osh user data — safety net in case a .forge-osh/ directory is
# accidentally created inside the repo root (e.g. if FORGE_CONFIG_DIR is
# set to the project dir during development).  These patterns are anchored
# to the repo root with a leading slash so they CANNOT match src/, Cargo.toml,
# or any other part of the codebase.
/.forge-osh/
/keys.json
/hooks.json
/permissions.json